dataList.content: They made for pathetic foes. That was absolutely nothing.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: The Tingtang Gang had tight control over this area. This is not going to be the end of―
Just then, more Tingtangers began showing up from the street corners.

dataList.title: Tingtang Gang
dataList.content: Who sent ya haricots to mess with us?!
We are the proud soldiers of Limbu― Hmgh…
Effie quickly covered Don Quixote’s mouth.

dataList.title: LCCB
dataList.content: Have you lost it? Do you want the entire District after us?
More are coming! Give us your command, Manager!
